                <p>Joseph Lamoliatte - Appointed Agt. by Cons. at Bordeaux</p>
                <p>P.C. Lanne was Act. Agent in June 1807.</p>
                <p>Bernard Chevalier Lanne, Agent 1845 to after 1853.</p>
                <p>Consul Sullivan reported on Jan. 1, 1854 that Mr. Furtado claimed he never had
                    the archives and did not act as Consul; that B.C. Lanne was acting V.C. by order
                    of Consul at Bordeaux and he had not removed him.</p>
